high_descs: Turn left, enter the room, turn right. Approach the bed, turn right. At the end of the bed, turn left. Reach the small shelf.
Grab the potato.
Turn around. Move forward a little and then turn right.
Place the potato in the pot.
Grab the potato and the pot.
Turn left, go to the wall. Turn left. Continue ahead until you pass the round diningtable, turn left. Reach the diningtable and turn left.
Place the pot and potato on the left side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Find a potato and a pot. Place them on the round dining table.

then take the pot move to reach the bed

after reach the hall in the diningtable

high_descs: Turn left, exit through the door and cross the hall to enter the shelf.
Stop in front of the nightstand and remove the potato from the nightstand.
Turn left to that you face the pot.
Place the potato into the pot on the bed.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn left and exit the bedroom, turn left and move toward the living room, coming to a stop in front of the diningtable.
Place the pot on the diningtable.
